msgstr "La version di cheste estension, teme o plugin e je stade eliminade dai autôrs e duncje e à ricevût limitazions de bande di Mozilla."

#: src/amo/pages/Block/index.js:221
msgid "This extension, theme, or plugin violates %(startLink)sMozilla's add-on policies%(endLink)s."
msgstr "Cheste estension, teme o plugin al viole lis %(startLink)spolitichis di Mozilla pai components adizionâi%(endLink)s."

#: src/amo/pages/Block/index.js:233
msgid "What does this mean?"
msgstr "Ce significhial?"

#: src/amo/pages/Block/index.js:239
msgid "Why does Mozilla restrict deleted add-ons?"
msgstr "Parcè Mozilla limitie i components adizionâi eliminâts?"

#: src/amo/pages/Block/index.js:245
msgid ""
"When the author deletes their add-on, it's no longer maintained or updated, which could compromise Firefox security, stability, or performance. To prevent this, the add-on will be restricted from "
"general use to protect Firefox users. For more information, please read %(supportStartLink)sthis support article%(supportEndLink)s."
msgstr ""
"Se l'autôr al elimine il so component adizionâl, chest nol ven plui mantignût o inzornât. Chest l podarès comprometi la sigurece, la stabilitât o lis prestazions di Firefox. Par protezi i utents di "
"Firefox e par impedî chestis situazions, a vignaran stabilidis limitazions su la utilizazion gjenerâl dal component adizionâl. Par vê plui informazions, lei %(supportStartLink)schest articul di "
"supuart%(supportEndLink)s."

#: src/amo/pages/Block/index.js:263
msgid "How does Mozilla enforce its policies?"
msgstr "In ce maniere Mozilla al apliche lis propriis politichis?"

#: src/amo/pages/Block/index.js:269
msgid ""
"When Mozilla becomes aware of add-ons, plugins, or other third-party software that seriously compromise Firefox security, stability, or performance and meet %(criteriaStartLink)scertain "
"criteria%(criteriaEndLink)s, the software may be blocked or restricted from general use. For more information, please read %(supportStartLink)sthis support article%(supportEndLink)s."
msgstr ""
"Tal moment che Mozilla al scuvierç che un component adizionâl, un plugin o un altri software di tiercis parts al rive a comprometi in maniere serie la sigurece, la stabilitât o lis prestazions di "
"Firefox e che al rispuint a %(criteriaStartLink)sdeterminâts criteris%(criteriaEndLink)s, al sarà pussibil che chel software al vegni blocât o limitât pal ûs public. Par vê plui informazions, lei "
"%(supportStartLink)schest articul di supuart%(supportEndLink)s."

